---
import td1 from '../../assets/tepung_daging/td1.jpeg'
import td4 from '../../assets/tepung_daging/td4.jpeg'
import garam from '../../assets/garam/garam_halus.jpeg'
// Hero Section dengan tagline kuat
---
<section class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-600 to-emerald-800 text-white overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
    <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1760159201329-521cd85a5bf9?ixlib=rb-4.1.0&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D&auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=1470');"></div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="container mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 py-16 md:py-24 relative z-10">
    <div class="max-w-3xl">
      <div class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 bg-white/20 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-6">
        Tangan Pertama · Tanpa Perantara · Sejak 2018
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight leading-tight">
        Bahan Baku Pakan Ternak Berkualitas untuk Bisnis Anda
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg md:text-xl text-emerald-50 leading-relaxed">
        Supplier terpercaya MBM, PMM, Garam Pakan, dan suplemen ternak. Langsung dari sumber, harga kompetitif, stok konsisten di 5 kota besar.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <a href="/products" class="btn bg-white text-emerald-700 hover:bg-emerald-50 font-semibold px-8 py-3">
          Lihat Produk Kami
        </a>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn bg-transparent border-2 border-white text-white hover:bg-white/10 px-8 py-3">
          Hubungi Sales
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Keunggulan / Value Propositions -->
<section class="section bg-white">
  <div class="container mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="flex gap-4 mt-6 mb-6">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-emerald-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-emerald-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg">Tangan Pertama</h3>
          <p class="text-muted mt-1 text-sm">Tanpa perantara, langsung dari sumber untuk harga terbaik</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="flex gap-4 mt-6 mb-6">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-emerald-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-emerald-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z"></path>
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg">5 Lokasi Gudang</h3>
          <p class="text-muted mt-1 text-sm">Bekasi, Bogor, Lampung, Medan, Surabaya - siap kirim cepat</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="flex gap-4 mt-6 mb-6">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-emerald-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-emerald-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-6 9l2 2 4-4"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg">Kualitas Terjamin</h3>
          <p class="text-muted mt-1 text-sm">Grade lengkap, spesifikasi jelas, untuk feedmill & poultry shop</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<!-- Sekilas CSN -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="container mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div>
        <div class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-4">
          Tentang Kami
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Sekilas CSN</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-muted leading-relaxed">
          CV. Cempaka Selaras Nusantara adalah supplier dan distributor bahan baku pakan ternak yang telah dipercaya sejak 2018. Kami berkomitmen menyediakan bahan baku berkualitas tinggi langsung dari sumbernya—tangan pertama tanpa perantara—agar pelanggan mendapatkan harga kompetitif dan pasokan konsisten.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-muted leading-relaxed">
          Melayani berbagai industri feedmill, poultry shop, dan pasar peternakan di Indonesia dengan produk berkualitas dan service terbaik.
        </p>
        <a href="/about" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 mt-6 text-emerald-600 font-medium hover:gap-3 transition-all">
          Selengkapnya tentang kami
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="relative">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1625246333195-78d9c38ad449?w=800" alt="Pakan Ternak" class="rounded-2xl shadow-xl w-full" loading="lazy" />
        <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -left-6 bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg max-w-xs">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-emerald-600">7+</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-muted mt-1">Tahun pengalaman melayani industri pakan ternak</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Produk Unggulan -->
<section class="section bg-white">
  <div class="container mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4">
    <div class="flex items-end justify-between gap-6 mb-8">
      <div>
        <div class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-4">
          Produk Kami
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Produk Unggulan</h2>
      </div>
      <a href="/products" class="btn btn-ghost text-emerald-600">Lihat Semua</a>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
      <article class="card overflow-hidden group hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <div class="relative overflow-hidden">
          <img src=`${td1.src}` alt="Meat Bone Meal" class="w-full h-48 object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="absolute top-3 right-3 bg-emerald-500 text-white text-xs font-semibold px-2 py-1 rounded">3 Grade</div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-5">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg">Meat Bone Meal</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted mt-2">Sumber protein hewani & mineral kalsium untuk formulasi pakan. Protein hingga 50%.</p>
          <div class="mt-4 flex items-center text-sm text-emerald-600 font-medium">
            <span>Lihat Detail</span>
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-1 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="card overflow-hidden group hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <div class="relative overflow-hidden">
          <img src=`${td4.src}` alt="Poultry Meat Meal" class="w-full h-48 object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="absolute top-3 right-3 bg-emerald-500 text-white text-xs font-semibold px-2 py-1 rounded">Protein 60-65%</div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-5">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg">Poultry Meat Meal</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted mt-2">Bahan protein hewani premium untuk unggas & ruminansia. Asam amino sempurna.</p>
          <div class="mt-4 flex items-center text-sm text-emerald-600 font-medium">
            <span>Lihat Detail</span>
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-1 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="card overflow-hidden group hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <div class="relative overflow-hidden">
          <img src=`${garam.src}` alt="Garam Pakan" class="w-full h-48 object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="absolute top-3 right-3 bg-emerald-500 text-white text-xs font-semibold px-2 py-1 rounded">4 Jenis</div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-5">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg">Garam Pakan</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted mt-2">Menunjang keseimbangan elektrolit & konsumsi pakan. NaCl 98%, tersedia berbagai ukuran.</p>
          <div class="mt-4 flex items-center text-sm text-emerald-600 font-medium">
            <span>Lihat Detail</span>
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-1 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="card overflow-hidden group hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <div class="relative overflow-hidden">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1582719471137-c3967ffb1c42?w=500" alt="CHITO FARM" class="w-full h-48 object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="absolute top-3 right-3 bg-amber-500 text-white text-xs font-semibold px-2 py-1 rounded">Suplemen</div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-5">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg">CHITO FARM</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted mt-2">Suplemen alami dari chitosan untuk meningkatkan imun & efisiensi produksi ternak.</p>
          <div class="mt-4 flex items-center text-sm text-emerald-600 font-medium">
            <span>Lihat Detail</span>
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-1 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>